# Issie Shared Signing Configuration

This file contains centralized signing configuration for all Issie projects.

## Structure

Each keystore group has:
- `issie.<group>.storeFile` - Keystore filename (in this directory)
- `issie.<group>.keyAlias` - Key alias
- `issie.<group>.storePassword` - Store password
- `issie.<group>.keyPassword` - Key password
- `issie.<group>.projects` - Comma-separated list of projects using this keystore

## Usage

Projects reference this file in their `build.gradle` to automatically load the correct signing config.

See `apply-signing.gradle` for the implementation.

## Security

This file contains passwords and should be:
- ✅ In `.gitignore` (never committed)
- ✅ Stored securely (1Password, etc.)
- ✅ Copied to `issie-shared/android/keys/` on setup

## Example

```properties
# Keystore group
issie.main.storeFile=uploadkeystore.jks
issie.main.keyAlias=key0
issie.main.storePassword=issiesays
issie.main.keyPassword=issiesays
issie.main.projects=issieboard,issievoice,issiesays

# Projects using this group
# - IssieBoard
# - IssieVoice
# - IssieSays
```
